author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
The wonderful Kill Team expansion kits keep on coming with the Blood & Zeal box bringing the Goremongers and Sanctifiers to the small-scale tabletop of the 41st Millenium. Let's check out the new Blood & Zeal game expansion as well as the box contents itself before we break into the two new Kill Teams!

Thanks to Games Workshop for the complimentary advance copy of the Box to review.
